South China Morning Post today provided a live blog of the press conference by Hong Kong’s wealthiest businessman Li Ka-Shing, after the announcement of 2016 earnings by CK Hutchison Holdings Ltd and Cheung Kong Property Holdings.
These are the first sets of full-year financial results by both companies since Li completed the reorganisation of his corporate empire.
Here are the highlights of what he said.














