李嘉誠


Born
(1928-07-29) 29 July 1928 (age 88)
Chaozhou, Guangdong, China


Citizenship
Hong Kong, China
Canada


Education
High school dropout[1]


Occupation
Chairman of CK Hutchison Holdings
Chairman of CK Property Holdings
Chairman of Li Ka Shing Foundation


