US$31.2 billion (March 2017)[2]


Spouse(s)
Chong Yuet Ming (m. 1963; d. 1990)


Children
Victor Li
Richard Li


Awards
Justice of the Peace (1981)
LL.D. (1986)
D. SSc (1994)







Li Ka-shing


